1)	The sub-menu for “Close and Rebook Loans & Collaterals” will be added below the “Cancel and Rebook Loans” option.
2)	The new screen will be created by duplicating the existing screen “Cancel and Rebook Loans” on LAVA, except for booking a return (PR & SR) instead of a cancel (CSL) before the rebooking, in the following sequence
a.	Book a pending return (PR), then wait few seconds as per G1 specification.
b.	Book a settled return (SR) then wait few seconds as per G1 specification.
c.	Book a new loan / collateral.
3)	The new screen should display and allow close-out and rebooking of both Loans and Collaterals.
4)	The screen should show settled Sec Lending transactions (Loans & Collaterals) only.
5)	The following transactions should be excluded from being displayed:
a.	Future Loans.
b.	Repo Loans
c.	Loans with pending returns (PR).
d.	LSS
e.	FICC
6)	The screen should default the Transmit Flag to “No” for booking both i.e., the return and subsequently the new loan / collateral.
7)	Except for the “Transmit Flag”, all other Return / Loan / Collateral attributes should be retained and remain unchanged. 
8)	The “Settlement Date” should be defaulted to the same day for both the close / return & rebook i.e.,
a.	The PR /SR should be booked with the current date as “Settlement Date”, also
b.	Also, the new Loan should be with the current date as “Settlement Date”.
9)	The selection criteria will be changed to “Loan / Collateral”.
10)	The label on the button will be changed to “Close & Rebook” 
11)	All the other underlying functionality, formatting and color-coding scheme will be duplicated. 
